Directed by Madhavan

Written by Madhavan. Anant Mahadevan. Rahul Pandey. Sreedevi Krishnan. Sukhmani Sadana. Anjali Nair. Anjali Nair

Star Madhavan(Nambi Narayanan). Simran(Meena Narayanan). Rajit Kapoor(Vikram A Sarabhai (Hindi / English Vers). Ravi Raghavendra(Vikram A Sarabhai (Tamil / Telugu Version)). Misha Ghoshal(Geeta Narayanan). Shyam Renganathan(Shankar). Muralidaran(Arunan). Karthik Kumar(P M Nayar). Sam Mohan(Unni). Rajeev Ravindranathan(Param). Dinesh Prabhakar(L D Gopal). Mohan Raman(Udupi Ramachandra Rao). Ron Donachie(Col. Cleaver). Phyllis Logan(Mrs. Cleaver). Vincent Riotta(Professor Luigi Crocco). Bijou Thaangjam(Studio Personnel).Jagan. Amaan(A.P.J. Abdul Kalam). Bhawsheel Sahni(Sartaj). Bhawsheel Sahani Singh(Sartaj). Shah Rukh Khan(Self (Guest Appearance)). Suriya(Self (Guest Appearance)). Jack Dimich(Professor Eugene Scott (as Zeljko Dimic)). Karina Matas Piper(Michelle). Hugo Alejo(Brian). Arnaud Humbert(Pierre). George Lasha(Alexander Dunayev). Abudhar Al Hassan(Studio Director). Pathy Aiyar(Satish Dhavan (Tamil)). Aleksandra(French Scientist). Arif(Guy at the wedding). Sowmyashree Belur(Unni’s wife). Joe Buell(American Agent). James Elia(Unni’s father in law). Emma Gojkovic(Elizabeth). Shyam Gopal(M L Sharma). Girish Gopalan(Pacifier). Shilpa Iyer(Studio Sound Engineer). Anurita Jha(Mariam Rashida). Veronika Kalandarishvili(Alexa). Lasha Kankava(Kremlin officer). Deepak Kripalani(Satish Dhavan (Hindi & English) (as Deepak Kriplani)). Kartik Krishnan(Surendran). Raam Kumar(Sekhar). Lucas(French Scientist 2). Ankith Madhav(Veer). Balaji Madhavan(Crew guy 2). Kartik Mane(Young Priest). A.R. Manikandan(Lightman 1). Midhun Venugopal(T.V. Reporter (as Midhun A.E.)). Vijalaxmi Mishrikoti(Fauzya Hassan). Prashant Nair(Aggressor). Prakash Nambiar(Doctor at Nambi’s house). Nambi Narayanan(Real Nambi Narayanan). Nibedita(Anchor’s Hmu). Sriram Parthasarathy(Barry Amaldev). Mahesh Pillai(Doctor at Latex Guesthouse). Shankar(Arunan’s Friend 1). Sumana Shankar(Bride’s mother). Nayana Shyam(Girl Crew). Viswanathan Sridhar(Nambi’s brother in law). Venkataraghavan Srinivasan(Officer 1). Sudhanshu(Arunan’s Friend 2). Andrew Sykes(Neil Armstrong). Luka Tarxanmouravi(Sven). Erekle Tsintsadze(French Agent). Abhirami Venkatachalam(Boyfriend Girl). Gaurav Venkatesh(Studio Personnel). Vladimir Vuckovic(Yuri).Prashant Walde. Yulian(French Scientist 1). Rick Zingale(Professor Chockmark)

Language Hindi. Tamil. Telugu. English. Kannada. Malayalam

Producers Alek Conic. Irakli Gogichadze. Smriti Jain. Madhavan. Arjun Madhavan. Sarita Madhavan. Gaurav Mishra. Varghese Moolan. Vijay Moolan. Prakash Nambiar. Natia Nikoleishvili. Umesh Pawar. Md. Hafizur Rahman. Yogiraj Shetty. Tushar Sood

Production Tricolour Productions .Varghese Moolan Pictures .Sarke Studio
